flowchart LR

    Proposal["1. Proposal Stage<br/>Broad intelligent study system<br/>AI tutoring + focus monitoring<br/>hardware-assisted interaction"]
    Foundation["2. Platform Foundation<br/>Authentication, courses,<br/>sessions, and study workspace"]
    Streams["3. Parallel Implementation Streams<br/>Web platform<br/>App services + persistence<br/>ML data + training"]
    Refinement["4. ML Refinement<br/>Calibration discipline, data growth,<br/>LOSO evaluation, tuning<br/>macro F1 improves from low 0.40s<br/>to low 0.70s across archived runs"]
    Pivot["5. Architecture Pivot<br/>Raspberry Pi path dropped<br/>Cloud-first inference adopted<br/>local FastAPI retained for development"]
    Final["6. Final Convergence<br/>Focus-aware study platform<br/>directional-attention subsystem<br/>integrated with dashboards,<br/>exam workflows, and gamification"]

    Proposal --> Foundation --> Streams --> Refinement --> Pivot --> Final

    Web["Web Platform<br/>Chat UI, study mode,<br/>dashboard, exam simulation"]
    Services["Application Services<br/>Cloud Functions, material indexing,<br/>chat orchestration, gamification"]
    ML["ML Pipeline<br/>Collection, validation,<br/>training, LOSO evaluation,<br/>runtime inference"]

    Streams --> Web
    Streams --> Services
    Streams --> ML

    Web --> Final
    Services --> Final
    ML --> Final

